{"TopicId":45067,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Picture help","CreatedByName":"Mr.Rocket","CreatedById":80241,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-09-05T23:24:09Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mr.Rocket","CreatedById":80241,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-09-05T23:24:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ei was just wondering how i post screenshots of ksp on the forums. i play on steam if that changes anythinghttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/images/smilies/k_tongue.gif\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Johnno","CreatedById":67618,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-09-05T23:34:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPictures need to be online somewhere, as I don\u0027t use steam anymore nor have ever posted pictures from there not sure how they\u0027re saved online, but you\u0027d need a link to the picture.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThen put them in a post by using [img ] link [/ img]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOtherwise you can use imgur or photobucket or any other free picture gallery service.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Toastie_Buns","CreatedById":75603,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-09-05T23:37:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mr.Rocket\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mr.Rocket\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ei was just wondering how i post screenshots of ksp on the forums. i play on steam if that changes anything\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEasiest thing to do is play the game and F12 when you want, then when you quit steam will bring up its screenshot manager. Then it\u0027s just a case of \u0022Show on disk\u0022 and selecting your image, then dragging those files over to imgur.com, since the site supports drag and drop.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESure saves surfing the filestructure of steam to find those innocuously named screenshot folders.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESecond method is to bring up Steam\u0027s \u0027Library\u0027, find Kerbal click it, then click Screenshot Library and \u0022Show on disk\u0022. Drag to imgur, upload.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPosting it on the forum is just a basic matter of using \u003Cimg src=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022\u003E tags, \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E [img] -insert url here- [/img] \u003C/pre\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDon\u0027t forget to use the DIRECT link imgur supplies you with. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENormal link: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/5fhjakhds\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/5fhjakhds\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDirect link: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/5fhjakhds\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/5fhjakhds\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHope that solves your problem. Happy capping, dudeski.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Giggleplex777","CreatedById":29829,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-09-05T23:42:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou use smilies simply by typing them in like this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[noparse]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-for